{"tid":224644,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"跑步加節食 但好似無咩效果","createTime":"2017-05-01T08:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T16:28:44.000Z","uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3adcb673d9db483663cfb0d7df092ee30b96be18","tid":224644,"uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:16:18.000Z","msg":"我已經跑左一個月步(每次30-45分鐘，睇下個日累唔累)      <br />\n另外，我亦都由過住每餐食兩碗飯變成食一碗飯(有時甚至唔食)<br />\n但感覺一個月嚟個身形都好似冇咩變化，我已經冇食零食，汽水都無咩點飲，有無巴絲話我知點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fe739cc132f8386c04f9026e4a1171ddd120c0","tid":224644,"uid":13126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:21:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed0e22beab1c01d3aae3eb5f16c543f3707d2c9d","tid":224644,"uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>介甜晚上唔妹食咁多飯.做下重訓，肌肉需要既能量大，可以幫你訓覺都有減脂效果<br />\n<br />\n唔知你幾肥，但正常一個月1-2KG都可以接受</blockquote><br />\n171 66kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n重訓姐係掌上壓個啲？<br />\n其實我未磅 但係睇落個肚腩仔好似無變過。。<br />\n唔該絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9953d8e726ac002ec26ac295e524b7f2c4f536","tid":224644,"uid":87748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:28:17.000Z","msg":"加強d運動強度 每個位都做少少 飲水為主 食野清淡d"},{"pid":"bfd1c3fd1696310953de733371282a748a9cdb53","tid":224644,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:29:28.000Z","msg":"一個月<br />\n<br />\n此貼已完"},{"pid":"8f3734457e0c442e8295498b4b6cc6c2eac26758","tid":224644,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:31:21.000Z","msg":"有無誡糖同starch？"},{"pid":"1d65411362a905d58f452a42311c9319ca96742d","tid":224644,"uid":13126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:34:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54f38007cbe2bec140161793b833cd59c495f52d","tid":224644,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:36:15.000Z","msg":"第一，亂咁節食，就算減到都好易反彈<br />\n二，你跑步有冇計心跳？運動時心跳要每分鐘 220-(年齡) x 60~80% 之內先可以最大化消脂效果，多過唔好，少過唔明顯<br />\n三，做埋gym，練肌肉，有助減肥"},{"pid":"f19134c18376c0c8ceae7de4a023f575b7a49702","tid":224644,"uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無誡糖同starch？</blockquote><br />\n甜野差唔多成個月無飲 淨係上星期同fd出街飲左杯珍珠奶茶。。<br />\n澱粉我諗就冇乜點戒。。。因為我係帶飯同夜晚通常食屋企 所以呀媽煮咩我食咩 但每餐已經食少左一碗飯。。。"},{"pid":"4832f7f9c9a980b9fbcfc8748de7a6fa8e5a1625","tid":224644,"uid":64413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:41:17.000Z","msg":"如果你冇介碳水化合物同糖此post 已完"},{"pid":"81bfc64ffb278709088733967f3bd1465d69733a","tid":224644,"uid":106278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:41:29.000Z","msg":"171 66kg 都叫肥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b73e8aa5269eda31be0ed075d21e8d75510d2e8","tid":224644,"uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一，亂咁節食，就算減到都好易反彈<br />\n二，你跑步有冇計心跳？運動時心跳要每分鐘 220-(年齡) x 60~80% 之內先可以最大化消脂效果，多過唔好，少過唔明顯<br />\n三，做埋gym，練肌肉，有助減肥</blockquote><br />\n我冇節食 只係食少左好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來要計心跳？咁我想問電話app個啲準唔準？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAnyway thank you 巴打"},{"pid":"facc8a4124c9abf7e55afb92a10bf0231aea3dc6","tid":224644,"uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:43:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>171 66kg 都叫肥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔算好肥 但個肚腩愈黎愈大 先決心跑下步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea2d7518e31d837fe2f2111392e4dacc40f43fe","tid":224644,"uid":95325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:43:40.000Z","msg":"持續咁做係會有效果 未必係肚腩細先代表減到<br />\n如果減重 每星期輕1-2磅已經夠<br />\n<br />\n同埋你平均每餐／日 食幾多蔬菜水果 肉類？"},{"pid":"3fb73507a8e5be2ccb69711789321dbfa1cfc37f","tid":224644,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:44:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2092e00e286a611837c40150bb97a9730dc57a61","tid":224644,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08a8b15fc49ca78aab00a1449363ca6737310aaf","tid":224644,"uid":27954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:47:39.000Z","msg":"真係有心減肥起碼要食少一半既野<br />\n睇上面話節食無用 跟本就係BULL SHIT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我靠跑步節食一個月減左起碼10磅"},{"pid":"7a0734b669a0522671180d0c8bdc92935e1e68a8","tid":224644,"uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:47:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>持續咁做係會有效果 未必係肚腩細先代表減到<br />\n如果減重 每星期輕1-2磅已經夠<br />\n<br />\n同埋你平均每餐／日 食幾多蔬菜水果 肉類？</blockquote><br />\n每日兩至三餐(有時就遲到唔食早餐)<br />\n水果我好少食。。但呀媽知我減肥都日日陪我食菜<br />\n就算有肉都係廋肉。。<br />\n定其實係因為我亂咁節食所以無咩效果。。？"},{"pid":"2dab3cd5e863b357f9cd3032ade74af0977951f5","tid":224644,"uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:48:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無誡糖同starch？</blockquote><br />\n甜野差唔多成個月無飲 淨係上星期同fd出街飲左杯珍珠奶茶。。<br />\n澱粉我諗就冇乜點戒。。。因為我係帶飯同夜晚通常食屋企 所以呀媽煮咩我食咩 但每餐已經食少左一碗飯。。。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />珍珠奶茶，抵你減唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續做死肥婆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1次姐唔好罵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我係巴"},{"pid":"f81b438bd319f044ab96e18b06718bb313d3154f","tid":224644,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:49:16.000Z","msg":"樓主住邊 一唔一齊跑步 我都要減"},{"pid":"eac4520cbd8dea7cfab48c1f3578704a9a30a1ca","tid":224644,"uid":27954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:49:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>持續咁做係會有效果 未必係肚腩細先代表減到<br />\n如果減重 每星期輕1-2磅已經夠<br />\n<br />\n同埋你平均每餐／日 食幾多蔬菜水果 肉類？</blockquote><br />\n每日兩至三餐(有時就遲到唔食早餐)<br />\n水果我好少食。。但呀媽知我減肥都日日陪我食菜<br />\n就算有肉都係廋肉。。<br />\n定其實係因為我亂咁節食所以無咩效果。。？</blockquote><br />\n咁無理由瘦唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但早餐一定要食"},{"pid":"5a6cfaf421a625edfd9251393e27a3c550e50bf6","tid":224644,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:51:11.000Z","msg":"跑步點樣節食 <br />\n我之前跑左一牌胃口就開始大"},{"pid":"615adfbb412e37214985f35e5c8f6ed3acacb036","tid":224644,"uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>持續咁做係會有效果 未必係肚腩細先代表減到<br />\n如果減重 每星期輕1-2磅已經夠<br />\n<br />\n同埋你平均每餐／日 食幾多蔬菜水果 肉類？</blockquote><br />\n每日兩至三餐(有時就遲到唔食早餐)<br />\n水果我好少食。。但呀媽知我減肥都日日陪我食菜<br />\n就算有肉都係廋肉。。<br />\n定其實係因為我亂咁節食所以無咩效果。。？</blockquote><br />\n咁無理由瘦唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但早餐一定要食</blockquote><br />\n其實我諗有輕到(未磅)<br />\n但個肚腩仔感覺上冇變過先上黎問下各位意見。。"},{"pid":"cdbd58f0760745d0bd3e0470bd374e12d38062ba","tid":224644,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:53:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一，亂咁節食，就算減到都好易反彈<br />\n二，你跑步有冇計心跳？運動時心跳要每分鐘 220-(年齡) x 60~80% 之內先可以最大化消脂效果，多過唔好，少過唔明顯<br />\n三，做埋gym，練肌肉，有助減肥</blockquote><br />\n我冇節食 只係食少左好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來要計心跳？咁我想問電話app個啲準唔準？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAnyway thank you 巴打</blockquote><br />\n按心口/按手度就最準，不過你做緊嗰時唔會分到心去數心跳<br />\n所以用手錶/app就好，都準嘅，唔會差太多<br />\n不過要注意用app嘅話周圍唔好太光，佢會check唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769668bac68a62c513e6fb8f6990a8135582239f","tid":224644,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:53:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c967c7e2003bdc70c75a4c1af39f241ad0b255d","tid":224644,"uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:53:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跑步點樣節食 <br />\n我之前跑左一牌胃口就開始大</blockquote><br />\n我係訓前捱餓 我係靠睇youtube啲美食影片望梅止渴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5440e5cfa588bcd125e18b9bc78663dfd8eff9fa","tid":224644,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:54:32.000Z","msg":"減肥黎講<br />\n游水效果好好多"},{"pid":"024497e80f1784874de8e6a9d2f4e7845be8efe4","tid":224644,"uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:56:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無誡糖同starch？</blockquote><br />\n甜野差唔多成個月無飲 淨係上星期同fd出街飲左杯珍珠奶茶。。<br />\n澱粉我諗就冇乜點戒。。。因為我係帶飯同夜晚通常食屋企 所以呀媽煮咩我食咩 但每餐已經食少左一碗飯。。。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />珍珠奶茶，抵你減唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續做死肥婆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1次姐唔好罵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我係巴</blockquote><br />\n我就咁既<br />\n早餐 八蚊蛋治+盒裝脫脂奶+三粒阿信屋果仁<br />\n岩小小肚餓拍多三粒果仁<br />\n午餐就盡量多菜少肉+走甜飲品<br />\n晏少少就拍條蕉<br />\n晚上就跑步situp<br />\n晚餐就強迫自己食菜先<br />\n後先食小小肉同極小飯<br />\n我咁做既so far不錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThank you巴打意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我會參考下你個減肥plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22241fc8f0dea54a448d470c8fb8f4a93d6db0dd","tid":224644,"uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一，亂咁節食，就算減到都好易反彈<br />\n二，你跑步有冇計心跳？運動時心跳要每分鐘 220-(年齡) x 60~80% 之內先可以最大化消脂效果，多過唔好，少過唔明顯<br />\n三，做埋gym，練肌肉，有助減肥</blockquote><br />\n我冇節食 只係食少左好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來要計心跳？咁我想問電話app個啲準唔準？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAnyway thank you 巴打</blockquote><br />\n按心口/按手度就最準，不過你做緊嗰時唔會分到心去數心跳<br />\n所以用手錶/app就好，都準嘅，唔會差太多<br />\n不過要注意用app嘅話周圍唔好太光，佢會check唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOk thank you brother <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7f35f4ad910cac57b40c338ef167c52f30e093","tid":224644,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:59:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跑步點樣節食 <br />\n我之前跑左一牌胃口就開始大</blockquote><br />\n我係訓前捱餓 我係靠睇youtube啲美食影片望梅止渴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我臨訓挨餓就訓唔到了<br />\n我身高體重同你差唔多<br />\n跑左幾個月腰大脾明顯幼左<br />\n見有效果飲食就無咩點理"},{"pid":"bca94b4f4c5f682fedeaa4613bc0aa0a1bb11d09","tid":224644,"uid":52875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:02:03.000Z","msg":"唉，我跑左兩個月都冇乜點輕過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但睇得出條腰側幼左，但個下腹好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就快想扔左個磅，廢事打擊毅力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cc4fd44a3ad4d7c70539a05894cdda459b77e0","tid":224644,"uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>跑步點樣節食 <br />\n我之前跑左一牌胃口就開始大</blockquote><br />\n我係訓前捱餓 我係靠睇youtube啲美食影片望梅止渴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我臨訓挨餓就訓唔到了<br />\n我身高體重同你差唔多<br />\n跑左幾個月腰大脾明顯幼左<br />\n見有效果飲食就無咩點理</blockquote><br />\n有效未得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAnyway 一齊加油"},{"pid":"0d1567a49fb38547fa83ead23b8cc1484f88ddfc","tid":224644,"uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉，我跑左兩個月都冇乜點輕過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但睇得出條腰側幼左，但個下腹好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就快想扔左個磅，廢事打擊毅力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一齊加油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n絲打你得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5ad4d51bafd2f654ad8678449501e9ad6137a9","tid":224644,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:09:51.000Z","msg":"試下google HICT啲人話減肥效果會好<br />\n我自己就未試過<br />\n可以從生活習慣入手 平時做多啲嘢 行多啲跑密啲keep住metabolic rate高"},{"pid":"0173f15ef768154ee31f6e87fe31f0a95e19b9df","tid":224644,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:11:01.000Z","msg":"你跑30-45分鐘計唔計拉筋<br />\n如果計嘅話就太少"},{"pid":"1f1adbd0b162da244c19ebc6d390cc2a9661cb5d","tid":224644,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:12:34.000Z","msg":"冇節食冇介口<br />\n跑下步舉下鐵<br />\n幾年減左10kg<br />\n個肚腩冇咁大<br />\n全身身瘦左<br />\n而家65kg<br />\n開始減唔到"},{"pid":"bc54f7c794057e2ba1d2f8508891d961bcaf5a23","tid":224644,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:31:24.000Z","msg":"食薯仔 健身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a864244bf89a50a086372a37c449113a3fbbd1","tid":224644,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:39:54.000Z","msg":"資料唔足, 但都試下答你<br />\n66KG 171CM 唔算好肥，睇磅數只係參考，不如量腰圍仲實際，睇到有無減到<br />\n你話跑咗個半月，但又無話幾耐跑一次，日日跑同一星期跑兩次已經差好遠<br />\n要食早餐，少鈉少糖，份量唔做突然減得太多，適當就好，少食多餐<br />\n叫你戒澱粉嘅人，同佢講句&quot;屌你老母死撚開啦&quot;就得，唔使再理佢<br />\n最好每次維持到有45-60分鐘一停嘅帶氧運動，唔夠氣做足60分鐘就轉急步行<br />\n配合適量重訓，增加消脂效果"},{"pid":"451bb8725162433f5ae9dc4747dfbde67ef68511","tid":224644,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:41:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下google HICT啲人話減肥效果會好<br />\n我自己就未試過<br />\n可以從生活習慣入手 平時做多啲嘢 行多啲跑密啲keep住metabolic rate高</blockquote><br />\n唔知樓主體質係點<br />\n唔好咁隨便叫人做HIIT"},{"pid":"419ad683d9d53e0fd8bef8d8b1c3995883979369","tid":224644,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:45:56.000Z","msg":"男人66kg正常啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef6f2793f4f9b89415bc8e03e76394896efbde6","tid":224644,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:49:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人66kg正常啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBMI正常<br />\n建議樓主直接做gym練肌肉重好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 減乜q<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63cff658df42558a0e2f7e83f44bafc7e927a200","tid":224644,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>男人66kg正常啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBMI正常<br />\n建議樓主直接做gym練肌肉重好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 減乜q<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗樓主係嫌自己有肚腩。<br />\n增肌對燒脂係有幫助，但淨做增肌對剷除已經積聚咗嘅脂肪唔顯著，所以開頭最好係主力帶氧配合重瞓，等脂肪燒得七七八八就改做主力重訓，修身型兼防反彈。"},{"pid":"fe269f713f2efac8c25f6068f68e137169cf3b8d","tid":224644,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:13:39.000Z","msg":"輕過你但都有個肚腩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到我都想搞一搞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ae2b3f0120d22668d29e1e39f504dbc2e1b3fb","tid":224644,"uid":23699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:16:55.000Z","msg":"咁都叫肥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53e1ca33d8ba8cdb3c8311577d4262bf9c339aa","tid":224644,"uid":16555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:17:34.000Z","msg":"中央肥胖唔等於肥"},{"pid":"f6b58da322863d83058d0ede768627d2f827e334","tid":224644,"uid":29711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:19:59.000Z","msg":"節食減唔到肥架，開頭兩個禮拜或者會有效嘅，之後咪照舊反彈返，而且戒錪粉質影響情緒同思考，隨時餓到個胃有事添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食嘅質量重要過份量<br />\n同埋減肥最緊要練肌肉，齋跑步減得到嘅有限"},{"pid":"9ec7492e7986c6a8fdc9455bf94c931212b7db0d","tid":224644,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:25:50.000Z","msg":"晚上唔食澱粉質，8點後唔再食野"},{"pid":"a8e50de728e573c2bf4d74d5c6ebe2fec3167d32","tid":224644,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:49:18.000Z","msg":"淨係節食呢樣都知你肯定失敗<br />\n<br />\n仲要跑步長期效率會降低"},{"pid":"3d28b7595dfdbe0b9e692f5b5137596a53890b0b","tid":224644,"uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:06:58.000Z","msg":"多謝各位巴絲意見！！"},{"pid":"2fe043920c934396c2bbb5ced456469839f62674","tid":224644,"uid":108234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>男人66kg正常啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBMI正常<br />\n建議樓主直接做gym練肌肉重好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 減乜q<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗樓主係嫌自己有肚腩。<br />\n增肌對燒脂係有幫助，但淨做增肌對剷除已經積聚咗嘅脂肪唔顯著，所以開頭最好係主力帶氧配合重瞓，等脂肪燒得七七八八就改做主力重訓，修身型兼防反彈。</blockquote><br />\n想問問重訓即係做gym?"}]}